{"tid":564208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司就梁振英UGL案不採法律行動  廉署結束調查","createTime":"2018-02-17T16:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T03:04:52.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"507d20cb8d7891b700ee7349cefe29f93ca09f30","tid":564208,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/005514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F005514_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=edbb3562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首梁振英涉及收取澳洲UGL公司5千萬元事件，有消息指律政司已作出決定。無綫新聞17日晚上引述消息指，律政司決定<span style=\"color: red;\">不就前特首梁振英收取澳洲公司UGL款項採取法律檢控行動</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">廉政公署亦已結束調查</span>。有立法會議員指若消息屬實，會令港人極度失望及震驚，稱律政司必須清楚交代法律理據。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英涉及收取澳洲UGL公司5千萬元事件於2014年被傳媒揭發，指他參選特首後曾收取澳洲公司UGL 400萬磅英磅而未有申報，其後有政黨向廉署舉報，收款事件橫跨其特首任期，事發至今逾三年，無綫17日晚引述消息指律政司決定不作檢控。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息，指律政司去年底聘用一名英國御用大律師審視報告並提供法律意見，最近收到回覆，英國御用大律師認為，梁振英與UGL在協議有效期間，作為特首身份並沒有做出任何不當或貪污受賄行為，建議毋須採取進一步法律檢控行動；又引述消息指，廉署審查貪污舉報諮詢委員會已知悉事件，廉署亦因應律政司的決定，結束UGL案的調查工作。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷今晚接受《蘋果》查詢時指，如果無綫新公布的消息屬實，相信會令港人感到極之失望和震驚，因為前特首梁振英的涉貪案，案情嚴重性遠超前特首曾蔭權，認為若律政司決定棄檢控，必須先進一步公開交代法律理據，讓公眾和專業人士評論其決定是否合理，「律政司過去就極大爭議的案件，都有公開法律意見，今次鄭若驊一定要交代清楚」。<br />\n<br />\n曾就UGL事件到廉署舉報的新民主同盟范國威回覆《蘋果》查詢時則指，若然無綫新聞消息屬實，將會予人廉署未有扮演應有角色的感覺，因為梁振英收取UGL巨款一事，明顯是大有問題，認為鄭若驊和廉署必須公開交代今次決定理據。<br />\n<br />\n廉署回覆《蘋果》查詢，指根據既定政策，廉署不會評論個別事件或調查工作，亦不會就個別媒體的揣測性報導作評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180218/57845966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57845966&d=LZHfcfJPDyqyHdImOaK7KPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=4506b17b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180218%2F57845966&h=ad29aa8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180218/57845966</a>"},{"pid":"7d75943d7ffa274a76b5d0194c307cfd525b82e1","tid":564208,"uid":28366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/005752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F005752_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=970ba8ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4fe7559fd70f9e98c35a8398de61807d34abf0c","tid":564208,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157ab97fb5739504a92173871260b6696e157cf7","tid":564208,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2a48300be5de1c8febfb333358f3d0e52b418e","tid":564208,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d845ccb996b91593daed4e80e8f0fb182849126","tid":564208,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4df4c8bca48e0df95415108f2b034192685757","tid":564208,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:03:52.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235b37cf71bab8c8b5fb0b9771139606db27cb3c","tid":564208,"uid":54733,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/attach/201011/mobile01-8e24e8981d9781f7743802ed943ba10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbna